Inventions[dnd-info]=Introducing the remarkable inventions of Genji Tink, a renowned inventor and master of arcane engineering. With a fusion of magic and mechanical ingenuity, Genji Tink has created a collection of extraordinary devices that push the boundaries of possibility. From enhancing one's abilities to traversing dimensions, his inventions offer adventurers new realms of exploration and power. Let us delve into the realm of his creations and discover the wonders that await. Behold, a glimpse into the inventive mind of Genji Tink and his extraordinary creations.;*ChronoLink Nexus Ethereal Pocket Portal* Crafted by the visionary inventor Genji Tink, the ChronoLink Nexus Ethereal Pocket Portal is a remarkable device that serves as a gateway between realms, allowing for swift traversal of space. Through a fusion of enchantments and advanced technology, this compact apparatus harnesses the esoteric energies of the cosmos, bending the fabric of reality. Loaded with a temporal cyrex crystal imbued with spatial coordinates, the ChronoLink Nexus enables daring adventurers to transcend the boundaries of mundane travel and explore alternate realities with unparalleled swiftness.;*The Exceedingly Elaborate Engine of Aetheric Disruption and Dimensional Dispersion* A specialized weapon that emits disruptive waves of aetheric energy, capable of destabilizing magical spells, dispelling enchantments, and neutralizing mystical defenses.;*The Incredibly Intricate Temporal Manipulation Mechanism* A timekeeping device imbued with magical enchantments, allowing users to manipulate and control the flow of time within a limited radius, altering perception or slowing down adversaries.;*The Exquisitely Elaborate Automaton of Temporal Synchronization and Companionship* A small, mechanical companion infused with artificial intelligence, designed to assist adventurers in various tasks, ranging from scouting and surveillance to providing medical aid or combat support.;*The Astoundingly Intricate Apparatus of Alchemical Synthesis and Elemental Transmutation* An advanced apparatus capable of combining various rare ingredients and substances to create potent potions, elixirs, and magical concoctions with enhanced effects and reduced side effects.;*The Transcendently Resplendent Apparatus of Aetheric Communication and Ethereal Transference* A communication device that utilizes aetheric frequencies to establish long-range, secure transmissions between individuals, bridging distances and overcoming barriers.;*The Magniloquent Energy Amplification Apparatus* A wondrous contraption designed to magnify and harness the latent energies of the cosmos, channeling them into a concentrated beam of awe-inspiring power.;*The Astoundingly Complex Cogitation Contrivance* An intricate mechanical marvel imbued with arcane algorithms and intricate cogwork, capable of solving the most perplexing riddles and conundrums known to sentient beings.;*The Harmoniously Resonating Harmonic Harmonizer* A melodic masterpiece that resonates with the celestial symphony of the cosmos, producing harmonies so captivating that they can sway the hearts of gods and mortals alike.;*The Multifarious Morphological Metamorphicator* A transformative apparatus capable of altering the physical form and appearance of objects, creatures, or even oneself, granting the ability to assume countless shapes and guises.;*The Astoundingly Proliferating Pneumatic Propulsion Peculiarity* A pneumatic-powered contraption that propels objects or individuals through the air with astonishing speed and grace, defying the limitations of gravity and defying conventional means of transportation.;*The Exquisitely Enigmatic Etheric Etheroscope* A mystical apparatus that pierces the veil between dimensions, allowing glimpses into realms beyond mortal perception, revealing arcane knowledge and unveiling hidden truths.;*The Marvelously Mechanized Matter Manipulation Mechanism* A mechanical marvel infused with arcane energies, capable of manipulating the very fabric of matter, transmuting elements, and reshaping the world around it with astonishing precision.;*The Astutely Astounding Astrological Astrolabe* An intricate astronomical instrument that charts the celestial bodies and predicts cosmic events with unparalleled accuracy, offering profound insights into the mysteries of the cosmos.;*The Incredibly Intricate Multi-Dimensional Quantum Harmonizer and Temporal Flux Regulator* Also known as the "Button." Its purpose is to emit a single, gentle pressable button that, when activated, produces a soothing and melodic chime.;*The Astoundingly Elaborate Universal Information Transmitter and Interpretive Receptor* These highly intricate spectacles feature an intricate network of microprocessors, quantum entangled lenses, and an advanced neural interface system. Their primary function? To provide the wearer with crystal-clear vision, correcting even the slightest visual imperfections and enhancing the perception of colors.;*Precise Automated Whisker Sensing Contraption* PAWS, an ingenious creation by Genji Tink. This delightful invention combines intricate clockwork mechanisms with state-of-the-art sensory technology to simulate the endearing movements and behaviors of a playful kitten. The P.A.W.S. Contraption brings joy and companionship to those who interact with it, showcasing the incredible fusion of cuteness and mechanical ingenuity.;*Electromagnetic Gigaflux Detectivators*These detectivators appear as mechanical glasses. On one eye, a spinning blue lense that slowly turns as a goofy satellite dish looking thing rotates above it. This mechanism is spring powered and needs wound. The dish amplifies vibrations in the ground and can be detected via faint electrical impulses emitted by the detectivators.;*Magneplates*These are small discs that can be used to electrically attract anything matching the electrical charge of a humanoid. When activated, they take two seconds to build up their attraction. Once attracted, the target must make a DC 19 strength check of be attracted to the surface these are on. The target becomes paralyzed for 1d8 minutes, when the batteries then run out. Damage caused to the target has a 50% chance to disable this effect.;*Spacetime Electromagnetostatic Quantum Geometric Waveform Alteration Yielder (SEQGWAY)*This is Genji's attempt at a 'world shrinker'. Rather than shrinking the world, it actually effects only the user rather than the world around them based on a d20 roll. This device requires a lot of energy.;-1 to 14: Do nothing;-15 to 17: Maulfunction;-18: Shrink the user.;-19 to 20: Grow the user;*Transdimensional Hyper-Conveyance Container of Multifarious Technological Marvels*This bag is full of various MacGyver type items that Genji may need for any situation. This includes paper clips, tape, writing utensils, gems, lenses, wire, knives, and more.

